  "title": "Resource Operations and Administrative Support",
  "description": "<p><strong>Resource Operations and Administrative Support – Singapore</strong><br />We are looking for a proactive and organised Resource Operations and Administrative Support professional to support manpower planning, vendor recruitment coordination, and day-to-day operational administration. This role ensures smooth resource workflows, effective coordination with recruitment vendors, and efficient operational support across teams.<br />Location: West of Singapore<br /><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>Resource & Operations Support</p><ul><li>Support resource planning, tracking manpower availability, and managing onboarding/offboarding processes.</li><li>Maintain accurate resource records, trackers, and documentation.</li><li>Assist in preparing operational reports, dashboards, and presentations.</li><li>Coordinate internal meetings, schedules, and correspondence.</li><li>Liaise with internal stakeholders to ensure smooth operational processes.</li></ul><p>Recruitment Support / Vendor Liaison:</p><ul><li>Liaise with external recruitment vendors/agencies for candidate submissions.</li><li>Screen resumes received from vendors and coordinate interview schedules.</li><li>Support hiring managers in scheduling and tracking recruitment activities.</li></ul><p>Administrative Support</p><ul><li>Provide general administrative support, including meeting coordination, documentation, and ad-hoc operational tasks.</li><li>Assist with reports, presentations, and other operational documentation as needed.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Bachelor’s degree in Business, Operations, HR, or related field.</li><li>At least 3 years of experience in operations, administrative support, or recruitment support.</li><li>Experience liaising with vendors and coordinating recruitment-related tasks is preferred.</li><li>Strong organisational, multitasking, and communication skills.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office, especially Excel and PowerPoint.</li></ul><p>This is a 1 year contract to start, convertible to permanent. </p>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 3,
